<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 18:18:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>通用汽车表示尽管面临挑战仍致力于中国业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-says-it-is-committed-china-operations-despite-challenges-2024-08-08/</link><description>通用汽车周四表示，尽管面临来自本土品牌的激烈竞争，该公司仍致力于在中国建立盈利且自我可持续的业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 16:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-says-it-is-committed-china-operations-despite-challenges-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：嘉吉内部备忘录描述了旨在精简公司的结构性改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/cargill-internal-memo-describes-structural-overhaul-streamline-company-2024-08-08/</link><description>据路透社和两名公司消息人士透露，全球贸易公司嘉吉公司在未能实现内部盈利目标后将进行结构性调整，计划将业务精简为三个部门，而不是五个部门。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:56:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/cargill-internal-memo-describes-structural-overhaul-streamline-company-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>举重-中国小将罗夺得女子59公斤级金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-luo-china-wins-womens-59kg-gold-medal-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国小将罗世芳周四在巴黎奥运会上以241公斤的总成绩夺得59公斤级奥运会举重冠军，刷新了抓举和挺举的奥运纪录。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-luo-china-wins-womens-59kg-gold-medal-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>谢跳水跳板金牌卫冕让中国队一路横扫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-xie-wins-mens-three-metre-springboard-gold-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国选手谢思怡在东京奥运会上获得最高荣誉后，阔别跳水项目两年，周四在巴黎奥运会上成功卫冕三米板跳水金牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-xie-wins-mens-three-metre-springboard-gold-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国因强迫维吾尔人劳动而禁止另外五家中国公司进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/society-equity/us-bans-imports-five-more-chinese-companies-over-uyghurs-2024-08-08/</link><description>据政府发布的消息称，美国周四因涉嫌侵犯维吾尔人人权而禁止另外五家中国公司进口产品，这是其从美国供应链中消除强迫劳动制造的商品的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:38:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/society-equity/us-bans-imports-five-more-chinese-companies-over-uyghurs-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪推出首款配备激光雷达传感器的车型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-ev-maker-byd-launches-first-model-with-lidar-sensor-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国电动汽车（EV）巨头比亚迪周四推出了新版Seal EV，这是该公司首款配备激光雷达传感器的车型。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-ev-maker-byd-launches-first-model-with-lidar-sensor-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国明阳签署意大利风力涡轮机工厂协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-mingyang-signs-italy-wind-turbine-plant-deal-2024-08-08/</link><description>意大利工业部周四表示，中国明阳智能能源公司、意大利能源公司Renexia和意大利工业部已签署建立风力涡轮机制造厂的协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-mingyang-signs-italy-wind-turbine-plant-deal-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>皮划艇-卡林顿领先新西兰四人夺得皮划艇金牌，德国队赢得男子比赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-carrington-leads-new-zealand-four-kayak-gold-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，新西兰选手丽莎·卡林顿 (Lisa Carrington) 率领女子皮划艇四名队员在马恩河畔韦尔斯航海体育场 (Vaires-sur-Marne Nautical Stadium) 夺得金牌，以另一场令人惊叹的表现，将她个人的奥运金牌数增加到六枚金牌和一枚铜牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-carrington-leads-new-zealand-four-kayak-gold-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>皮划艇——新西兰在巴黎奥运会女子皮划艇四人组500米决赛中夺得金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-new-zealand-win-gold-womens-kayak-four-500m-final-paris-olympics-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，新西兰在马恩河畔瓦雷斯航海体育场举行的女子皮划艇四人组 500 米决赛中获得奥运会金牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:50:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-new-zealand-win-gold-womens-kayak-four-500m-final-paris-olympics-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>英国航空将于 10 月 26 日起停止飞往北京的航班</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/british-airways-halt-flights-beijing-oct-26-2024-08-08/</link><description>英国航空公司周四表示，由于欧洲航空公司因禁止飞越俄罗斯领空而苦苦挣扎，该公司将于 10 月 26 日至 2025 年 11 月期间停止飞往北京的航班，但未详细说明原因。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/british-airways-halt-flights-beijing-oct-26-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>巴黎奥运会皮划艇——中国队夺得男子皮划艇双人500米金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-china-win-gold-mens-canoe-double-500m-paris-olympics-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，中国队在马恩河畔瓦雷斯航海体育场举行的男子皮划艇双人500米比赛中获得奥运会金牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:46:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/canoeing-china-win-gold-mens-canoe-double-500m-paris-olympics-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球——中国队挺进决赛 志在包揽金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-china-reach-mens-final-with-win-over-feisty-france-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国队周四在巴黎奥运会上闯入男女乒乓球团体决赛，他们的目标是赢得最后两枚金牌，完成本届奥运会五枚金牌的横扫。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 11:41:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-china-reach-mens-final-with-win-over-feisty-france-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>减肥药助力礼来业绩 2024 年预测上调 30 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/eli-lilly-raises-annual-profit-forecast-zepbound-quarterly-sales-cross-1-billion-2024-08-08/</link><description>礼来公司备受追捧的减肥药 Zepbound 的生产能力提高，促使该公司周四将年销售额预期提高了 30 亿美元，其股价也跃升了 14%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:51:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/eli-lilly-raises-annual-profit-forecast-zepbound-quarterly-sales-cross-1-billion-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场依然坎坷，等待就业现实检验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>尽管利润大幅下滑，中国芯片制造商中芯国际第二季度业绩仍超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/smic-posts-59-fall-q2-profit-yet-beats-expectations-2024-08-08/</link><description>中芯国际周四公布第二季度净利润下降 59.1%，尽管这家中国最大的芯片代工厂的业绩超出预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 10:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/smic-posts-59-fall-q2-profit-yet-beats-expectations-2024-08-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>